setMarkerAlphaLocal 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Sets the marker alpha. The marker is only modified on the computer 
 where the command is called. When alpha equal one, the marker is visible 
, but if alpha equal zero, then the marker is invisible. Alpha can be numbers 
 and fractions.  
Syntax:  
 marker setMarkerAlphaLocal alpha 
Parameters: 
marker: String - 
alpha: Number - 
Return Value: 
 Nothing